  <section class="rules" id="rules">
    <div>
      <h3>Rules</h3>
      <p>
        Breakfast is only offered at Bielski Guesthouse and Bielski Lawendowa Rooms. Breakfast could be provided at the
        other properties upon request. Smoking is strictly prohibited on all properties. Smoking is only permitted at
        Bielski Guesthouse terrace on the top floor.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <h4><i class="fas fa-check-square"></i> Check-in/Check-out</h4>
          <p>Normal Check In time starts at 15:00. Check-out is at 10:00.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4><i class="fas fa-hand-sparkles"></i> Housekeeping</h4>
          <p>
            Housekeeping is provided daily between the hours of 12:00 to 15:00. We kindly ask you to remain out of the
            Guesthouse or remain in your room at this time.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4><i class="fas fa-luggage-cart"></i> Luggage</h4>
          <p>
            You may store your luggage before the check-in and after check-out for as long as you need to.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4><i class="fas fa-walking"></i> Self check-out</h4>
          <p>
            Please, place your room keys into the box located at the reception. Or leave it in the box at the
            self-check-in box at Ogarna Apartments
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4><i class="far fa-clock"></i> Late check-out time</h4>
          <p>
            Late check-outs are not permitted, however should you need some extended time, please notify the host.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4><i class="fas fa-house-user"></i> Prolonging your stay</h4>
          <p>
            Kindly contact us if you would like to prolong your stay. Your request will be satisfied upon room
            availability.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4><i class="fas fa-volume-mute"></i> Quiet hours</h4>
          <p>
            From 22:00 to 7:00.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h5><i class="fas fa-user-friends"></i> Other visitors</h5>
          <p>
            All visitors who are not mentioned in the reservation must vacate the premises by 22:00. In case of
            violation, the main guest will be fined.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4><i class="fas fa-glass-cheers"></i> Parties</h4>
          <p>
            Loud parties are not welcomed at all properties
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4><i class="fas fa-key"></i> Lost keys</h4>
          <p>
            The cost for replacement of lost room keys is 100 zl.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h4><i class="fas fa-bomb"></i> Emergency situations</h4>
          <p>
            In all urgent situations we recommend contacting us directly.
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
